acity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.4\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"card col-md-12 col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n              <h3 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mt-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\"><b>Work Experience</b></h3>\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n              </h5>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5 active\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                09/2015 - 07/2022\n              </h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg item-wrapper\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>Assistant&nbsp;Professor</b>, Robotics &amp; Mechatronics Department, School of Engineering and Digital Sciences, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan.<br><br>Research Focus:<br>- Specialized in machine learning and signal processing for real-time BrainComputer/Machine Interfaces.<br>- Advanced deep learning applications to ensure model generalizability across&nbsp;different sessions and subjects.<br>- Conducted research on improving the accuracy and efficiency of predictive models.<br>- Implemented machine learning solutions in various practical applications,&nbsp;enhancing the performance of systems in real-world scenarios.<br><br>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div><div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                08/2022 - present\n              </h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg item-wrapper\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>\n                Associate Professor</b>, Robotics &amp; Mechatronics Department, School of Engineering and Digital Sciences, Nazarbayev University, Kazakhstan.<br><br><i>Research Focus:<br></i>- Leading research in advanced machine learning and signal processing to&nbsp;decode brain data for brain-machine interfaces.<br>- Optimizing deep learning models to achieve general applicability across various domains, focusing on robustness and scalability.<br>- Developing innovative algorithms for pattern recognition, predictive modeling,&nbsp;and anomaly detection.<br>- Applying machine learning techniques to solve complex problems in diverse fields, including healthcare, robotics, and environmental monitoring.<br>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">05/2018 - 07/2018</h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg item-wrapper\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>\n                Visiting Professor</b>, Department of Electrical Engineering &amp; Computer Science, University of Houston, Houston, Texas, USA.<br><br>Research Focus:<br>Cortical source imaging of electroencephalographic signals in patients with stroke to examine neural correlates of brain plasticity pre and post-clinical trials with BMI actuated exoskeleton.<br>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div><div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">05/2014 - 09/2015</h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg item-wrapper\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>NIH Postdoctoral Research Fellow II</b>, Department of Electrical Engineering &amp; Computer Science, University of Houston, Houston, Texas, USA.<br><br>Research Focus:<br>Conducted research on developing brain machine interfaces to control therapeutic exoskeletons, aiding patient rehabilitation by exploring crucial&nbsp;brain functions for effective BMI interactions. Led research on the mirror&nbsp;neuron system’s impact on infants' motor learning using non-invasive methods,&nbsp;analyzing neural pathways to understand behavioral patterns. Developed&nbsp;precise methods for EEG source localization and enhanced connectivity&nbsp;analysis to map complex brain networks. Applied machine learning and<br>data analysis techniques to advance understanding in various neuroscience&nbsp;projects, demonstrating expertise in data-driven approaches to solve complex problems.<br>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3 \" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">01/2014 - 05/2014</h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0 item-wrapper\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>\n                Research Scientist,&nbsp;</b>Department of Neurology, Samsung Medical Center, Sungkyunkwan University, Seoul, South Korea. <br><br>Research Focus:<br>- Utilized advanced machine learning techniques for comprehensive ECoG&nbsp;data analysis, including time-series analysis and pattern recognition.<br>- Developed machine learning models to identify patterns and anomalies in EEG &amp; MEG recordings, aiding in pinpointing epileptogenic zones and refining&nbsp;surgical treatments for refractory focal epilepsy.<br>- Collaborated with medical teams in presurgical evaluations for patients with treatment-resistant epilepsy, integrating machine learning insights to improve&nbsp;accuracy<br>- Leveraged expertise in ECoG and machine learning to provide data driven insights that enhanced patient treatment plans.<br></p>\n            </div>\n          </div><div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3 \" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">05/2011 - 12/2013</h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0 item-wrapper\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>Senior</b>&nbsp;<b>Research Scientist,&nbsp;</b>Daegu Gyeongbuk Institute of Science and Technology, South Korea.&nbsp;<br><br>Research Focus:<br>- Applied kernel-based learning algorithms and neural networks for BCIs to&nbsp;control neuro-rehabilitation devices.<br>- Researched variabilities to improve fNIRS-based BCI performance using advanced statistical methods and time-series analysis.<br>- Enhanced non-invasive BCI paradigms with deep learning techniques, including ERP-based and Sensory-Motor Rhythms-based BCIs.<br>- Contributed to creating a Hybrid BCI system integrating brain hemodynamic&nbsp;and electrical signals, leveraging machine learning for signal fusion and pattern recognition.<br></p>\n            </div>\n          </div><div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3 \" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">02/2010 -05/2011</h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0 item-wrapper\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>Postdoctoral Research Fellow,&nbsp;</b>Daegu Gyeongbuk Institute of Science and Technology, South Korea.<br><br>Research Focus:<br>- Investigated key neural signal patterns using clustering and dimensionality&nbsp;reduction techniques.<br>- Developed semi-supervised feature selection and classification algorithms to&nbsp;enhance prediction accuracy.<br>- Conducted long-term developmental assessments of children with ADHD,&nbsp;employing machine learning models for longitudinal data analysis with Daegu&nbsp;University’s neurorehabilitation center.<i><br></i></p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
