, Seoul, South Korea.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div><div class=\"row justify-content-left item features-without-image mt-0 mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n              <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>Occasional Reviewer</b><div><b><br></b></div></h5>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg item-wrapper\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">#IEEE Transactions on Neural Networks and Learning Systems.<br><br>#IEEE Journal of Biomedical and Health Informatics.<br><br>#IEEE Transactions on Systems, Man, and Cybernetics: Systems.<br><br>#Brain Research, Elsevier.<br><br>#Neuroimage, Elsevier.<br><br>#Medical Engineering and Physics, Elsevier.<br><br>#Medical &amp; Biological Engineering &amp; Computing, Springer.<br></p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          \n\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
